type Symbol struct {

我们可以编写 Go 代码来访问和使用 `PackageSymbols` 这个 map：

```go
package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"go/src/cmd/vendor/golang.org/x/tools/internal/stdlib" // 假设你的项目结构可以访问到这个路径
)

func main() {
	archiveTarSymbols, ok := stdlib.PackageSymbols["archive/tar"]
	if ok {
		fmt.Println("Symbols in archive/tar package:")
		for _, symbol := range archiveTarSymbols {
			fmt.Printf("  Name: %s, Kind: %s, Value: %d\n", symbol.Name, symbol.Kind, symbol.Value)
		}
	} else {
		fmt.Println("archive/tar package not found in manifest.")
	}

	bufioWriterMethods := filterSymbols(stdlib.PackageSymbols["bufio"], "Method", "(*Writer).")
	fmt.Println("\nMethods of *bufio.Writer:")
	for _, symbol := range bufioWriterMethods {
		fmt.Printf("  Name: %s, Value: %d\n", symbol.Name, symbol.Value)
	}
}

// 辅助函数，用于过滤特定类型和前缀的符号
func filterSymbols(symbols []stdlib.Symbol, kind string, prefix string) []stdlib.Symbol {
	var filtered []stdlib.Symbol
	for _, symbol := range symbols {
		if symbol.Kind == kind && (prefix == "" || strings.HasPrefix(symbol.Name, prefix)) {
			filtered = append(filtered, symbol)
		}
	}
	return filtered
}

```
